snippet.title: Motocross #14 - VC 4000
snippet.description: This simple dragracing game has two dificulty modes, with one or two player modes. If you are too fast on the throttle you will be disqualified. You can blow or stall your engine if you shift your gears too fast or too slow. There are four gears to go through. Fun gameplay but not too hard. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2014/04/motocross-14-vc-4000.html
